        "label": "TextBlock5",
        "sanitize": false,
        "text": "<h4><strong>Transportation, Meals and Accomodation</strong></h4>\n<p class=\"p1\">Transportation and meal costs may be considered when the purpose of the trip is to escort the child to treatment or medical appointments related to the disability. Transportation costs paid to these appointments (e.g. car, bus, train, etc.) are allowable at actual cost. You will be reimbursed at $0.40 per kilometre for the use of a private car. Meals are allowable for the child and parent(s).</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Please note that loss of pay as a result of having to take your child for treatment is not an eligible expense.</p>",
